Bounty market pricing structure
Ideally, we control pricing like Metamask advanced gas pricing. Let DAOs choose to go over the limit to guarantee priority and attract top talent. But we will have to set minimums and base rates to do that. We can calculate base rates using the following criteria
- type of work
- expertise level
- number of contributors available at the time
- how much that type of work normally earns

We’ll need some data to do that somewhat accurately. So I opted for selectors on the form to extract valuable data points about how DAOs assign value to their bounties / expertise of contributors. We can then benchmark it all behind the scenes, teach the Ai and create price multipliers / base rates.
